title: Big Tech's market dominance spurs numerous U.S. antitrust probes
text: The U.S. Justice Department is expected to file a lawsuit against Alphabet Inc's Google on Tuesday in what could be just the first in a series of legal salvos against high-profile tech companies.

title: European Data Regulators Are Looking Into Instagram Now
text: Some younger Instagram users were converting their accounts to business accounts, compromising their contact information in the process.
